quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,80,"Kaya iwe uwapemphera chikhululukiro kapena usawapemphere, ngakhale iwe utawapemphera chikhululukiro kokwana makumi asanu ndi awiri, Mulungu sadzawakhululukira chifukwa iwo sanakhulupilire mwa Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake. Ndipo Mulungu satsogolera anthu ochita zoipa"
  9,81,"Iwo amene adasiyidwa m’mbuyo adasangalala chifukwa cha kukhala kwawo pambuyo pa Mtumwi wa Mulungu, iwo amadana ndi kukamenya nkhondo ndi chuma chawo ndiponsoiwoeniyokhazikitsaulamulirowa Mulungundipo iwo adati, “Musapite ku nkhondo chifukwa kuli kutentha kwambiri.” Nena, “Moto wa ku Gahena ndi wotentha kwambiri,” iwo akadangozindikira"
  9,82,Motero iwo aseke pang’ono ndi kudzalira kwambiri ngati malipiro a ntchito zimene adachita
  9,83,"Ngati Mulungu akubweretserani gulu lina la iwo ndipo akapempha chilolezo kuti atuluke; nena, “Inusimudzatulukandiinekapenakukamenyankhondondi adani pamodzi ndi ine. Inu munasangalatsidwa kukhala ku nyumba kwanu pa nthawi yoyamba ndipo khalani pamodzi ndi anthu otsalira m’mbuyo.”"
  9,84,"Iwe usampempherere aliyense wa iwo amene afa, ndipo usadzaime pa manda ake. Ndithudi iwo sanakhulupirire mwa Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake ndipo adafa ali ochita zoipa"
  9,85,Ndipousalolekutichumandianaawokutizikudabwitse iwe. Cholinga cha Mulungu ndi kuwalanga iwo ndi izi m’moyo uno ndikuti mizimu yawo idzachoke ali anthu osakhulupirira
  9,86,"Ndipo pamene Mutu uvumbulutsidwa kuwauza kuti akhulupirire mwa Mulungu ndi kuti amenye nkhondo limodzi ndi Mtumwi, anthu olemera pakati pawo amakupempha kuti, asakamenye nawo ndipo amati: “Tisiye ife tikhale pamodzi ndi anthu okhala m’mbuyo.”"